<H3> <TI>   UNPROFOR Troops in `Street Fight' With Police </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0302125394 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 3 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0302125394 </F>
<F P=104>  Skopje MILS-NEWS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "UNPROFOR Soldiers Fight Against </F>
Police"] 
  [Text] An incident took place at the Skopje city square, 
during the night between Friday and Saturday, last week, 
involving UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] soldiers and Macedonia 
police officers. Unofficially, about 20 UNPROFOR soldiers and 9 
policemen started a street fight. Neither the Macedonian Police 
Department, nor the UNPROFOR Headquarters have so far issued any 
official announcement. 

</TEXT>

