<F P=100> YUGOSLAVIA </F>
<F P=101> Kosovo </F>
<H3> <TI>   Serb Authorities Close 70 Albanian Enterprises </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0102195694 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1835 
GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0102195694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Serbian authorities in Kosova are obstructing 
every kind of endeavor by Albanians. Based upon orders from the 
Serbian leadership in Belgrade, 70 Albanian private enterprises 
have been closed in various centers of Kosova in the last 15 
days. 

</TEXT>

