----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|SLD               |&gt; 25               |24                |19                | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|PSL               |20                |19                |118               | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|UD                |16                |14                |14                | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
