|KLD               |7                 |6                 |5                 | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Nonparty Bloc in  |3                 |4                 |5                 | 
|Support of Reforms|                  |                  |                  | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 



</TEXT>

