  [Text] A short while ago we received via fax a copy of the 
following open letter addressed today by the Social Democracy 
Party of Romania [PDSR] to the chairmen of the PNTCD [National 
Peasant Christian-Democratic Party], PD-FSN [Democratic 
Party-National Salvation Front], UDMR [Democratic Union of 
