<F P=102>  AU0302154394 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 
1400 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0302154394 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest Radio Romania Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Romanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Prime Minister Nicolae Vacaroiu met with the NATO 
under secretary for political affairs, Mr. Gebhardt von Moltke, 
at Victoria Palace today. 
  After the end of the talks, a brief news conference was held 
within the framework of which Prime Minister Nicolae Vacaroiu 
emphasized the importance of this event for Romania, which 
represents the second stage of the Partnership for Peace, namely 
the preparation of the presentation document. 
  In his turn, the guest expressed satisfaction with the warm 
reception given him, with cooperation with Romania, and with the 
stage of preparations, which Romania is making to ensure better 
cooperation with NATO. 

