  [Excerpt] Bratislava, Feb 3 (CTK) -- [passage omitted] 
Slovakia overdrew the credit in the clearing with the Czech 
Republic by $50 million, Vice-Governor of the Slovak National 
Bank (NBS) Marian Jusko tells the opposition SME. The balance 
